Type of Feat: Class
Specifics: You summon a celestial spirit to watch over you and your allies within 30 feet. You and your allies present when the spirit is summoned gain fast healing 10 and a ward against death. If those warded against death drop to 0 or fewer hps the spirit revives that character. The character revived heals an amount equal to twice your paladin level. This is an instantly activated ability.
Use: Selected.